------------------------------------------------*/

This project is still in its initial stages of development. Progress continues whenever I have the time to work on it.


/* -----------------------------------------------
	Requirements
------------------------------------------------*/
node.JS + socket.io


/* -----------------------------------------------
	Setup
------------------------------------------------*/
Since this is a multiplayer game, you must start the server by running server.js with node.JS. You must also be running a web server. Have clients load the main index.html.


